title: Dementium - The Ward playthrough
description: I saw this game in a top 5 most impressive graphics for a DS game Youtube video and thought it looked cool as hell, so I wanted to play it. Turns out it is pretty neat. I wanted to play a relatively short game this time, so this fit that need perfectly. Now I want to play the sequel, which apparently has a PC port!
